1. ng add @angular-eslint/schematics
2. npm install prettier --save-dev
3. npm install prettier-eslint eslint-config-prettier eslint-plugin-prettier --save-dev
4. in eslint.config.js add 
    - const eslintPluginPrettierRecommended = require('eslint-plugin-prettier/recommended')
    - eslintPluginPrettierRecommended (add at the end)